description: Design: Borderless Display: The Motorola G85 5G features an innovative borderless design with a curved display that seamlessly blends into the back, enhancing its modern aesthetic. Material Options: Choose between sophisticated vegan leather finishes for a soft touch or a sleek PMMA material for an elegant look. Display: Large Screen: Enjoy a vibrant 6.7-inch borderless pOLED display that brings movies, shows, and games to life. High Refresh Rate: The 120Hz refresh rate ensures smooth scrolling and fluid navigation, perfect for gaming and browsing. Audio: Stereo Speakers: Experience high-quality sound with two powerful stereo speakers for enhanced clarity. Dolby Atmos: Enjoy multidimensional audio with Dolby Atmos technology, providing richer bass and immersive sound for your media. Camera System: 50MP Main Camera: Features a Sony LYTIA 600 sensor and Quad Pixel technology for sharp, vibrant photos in any lighting. Versatile Photography: Includes an ultra-wide-angle lens for expansive shots and a macro lens for close-up details. Low-Light Performance: Advanced features enable clear photos and videos even in dim conditions. Photo Optimization: Integrated Auto Adjust feature with Google Photos instantly enhances color and lighting for perfect shots. Performance: Powerful Processor: Powered by a Snapdragon processor, the G85 delivers optimized performance for multitasking and gaming. Generous Storage: Comes with 256GB of internal storage and 8GB of RAM, plus Memory Expansion for added speed and efficiency. Battery Life: Long-lasting Power: Equipped with a 5,000 mAh battery that supports all-day usage. Fast Charging: The 33W TurboPower charger enables quick recharging, minimizing downtime. The Motorola G85 5G combines cutting-edge design, immersive entertainment features, and a powerful camera system, making it an excellent choice for users seeking performance and style.
